Surf Ninjas;;1993;;PG;;Action,Adventure,Comedy;;5.1;;Neal Israel;;Ernie Reyes Sr.,Rob Schneider,Ernie Reyes Jr.,Nicolas Cowan,John Karlen,Oliver Mills,Jonathan Schmock,Neal Israel,Vladimir Parra,Brandon Karrer,Dathon Aragon,Phillip Bayless,Philip Tan,Keone Young,Romy Walthall,Rachel Kolar,Yoni Gordon,Sritao Thepchasoon;;Brothers Johnny, an adolescent surf talent, and Adam, a preadolescent video-game addict, grow up care-free in California as adopted sons of Marines veteran Mac, inseparable friends of wacky local lout Iggy. Colonel Chi's military reign of terror culminates in their tiny birth-land, island state Patu San, off the Viet Nam coast. Former royal guards officer Zatch comes to summon the brothers to return and restore the pacific monarchy, because they are the sons of the murdered king, whom Mac took in exile for safety. They are joined on the adventurous journey by a bored Californian police detective whose attention was drawn by the ninja team that failed, thanks to Zatch, to murder the brothers in Mac's home.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0108258/